## Linear Integration

**Team:** Yukta-athanor | **Project:** {{PROJECT}}

The Linear MCP's `state` parameter fuzzy-matches status names. When multiple
statuses share the same type (Triage/Backlog/Ideation/Icebox are all type
"backlog"), name-based moves can land in the wrong status. **Always use the
UUID for backlog-type and canceled-type statuses.**

